---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Why Our Series C Funding Round Changes People's Whole Perspective of Our Company - parcelLab" description="Mike Harris, VP Global Sales, reflects on parcelLab's $112 million Series C funding and its impact on hiring, product development, and global growth.">
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
      <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>Back to blog</a>
      <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
      <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Why Our Series C Funding Round Changes People's Whole Perspective of Our Company</h1>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
        <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab</strong></span><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
        <time datetime="2021-07-16">July 16, 2021</time><span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span><span>4 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div></div></section>
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24"><div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">Mike Harris, VP Global Sales, reflects on parcelLab's $112 million Series C funding announcement and its organizational impact. The capital injection accelerates hiring, strengthens recruitment, and validates the company's market position.</p>
      <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Key Quote</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"When you can tell candidates that we've just raised $112 million, it changes their perspective of parcelLab."</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">-- Mike Harris, VP Global Sales</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Immediate Impact</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">The funding enhances credibility with both prospective clients and partners. The partnership with Insight Partners, a prominent B2B SaaS venture firm, boosts the company's profile in North America. parcelLab already partners with 500+ brands globally.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Product Development Acceleration</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">The investment enables faster product development for existing and new customers. The company maintains ambitions as the global leader in Operations Experience while remaining focused on European growth.</p>
      <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Digital-First Sales Strategy</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Harris advocates for flexible work arrangements empowering teams to determine working locations. This approach simplifies scaling in new markets without establishing physical offices, while still valuing periodic in-office collaboration for sales development teams.</p>
      <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">Harris expresses confidence in team resilience and enthusiasm about the funding's potential impact on customers and partners going forward.</p>
    </div></section>
    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
